Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.12,0:00:03.58,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oh…\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:21.83,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You were doing so well earlier, too…\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.77,0:00:39.42,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Uh… hey!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:42.80,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Since we’re taking a break, why don’t I get you all some drinks?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:47.76,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:02.39,Kaho,,0,0,0,,…Kozue-senpai.\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:12.07,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Hup…\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:16.71,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Um…\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:23.27,Kaho,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I also think you’re working yourself too hard, Kozue-senpai.\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:29.19,Kaho,,0,0,0,,That’s why I want to do anything I can to support you.\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:35.53,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Kozue-senpai…\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.63,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:46.99,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Come on, there’s no way I could believe that when the look on your face says otherwise.\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.67,0:04:51.33,Kaho,,0,0,0,,That’s why we’re really worried about you two.\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:55.06,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Hey, Senpai.\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:59.05,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I’m not just here to listen to you, you know?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:02.25,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, I might even be able to help you.\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:05.95,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Here, I’ll be your roadside flower and lend you an ear.\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:16.33,Kaho,,0,0,0,,The second time…?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:06.54,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Kozue-senpai…\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:20.49,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But… why…?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:36.00,Kaho,,0,0,0,,But what about Tsuzuri-senpai…?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:34.53,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Why?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:38.90,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that!?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:41.26,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I don’t understand at all!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:48.40,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Even if you didn’t win, you still gave it everything you had, so as long as Tsuzuri-senpai refused the scouting offer…\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:51.03,Kaho,,0,0,0,,as long… as…\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:46.13,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Kozue-senpai!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:50.65,Kaho,,0,0,0,,That doesn’t make any sense!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:55.26,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Didn’t you say you were rejecting their scouting offer this time!?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:06.37,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Winning… Love Live!...\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:34.53,Kaho,,0,0,0,,…So you had times like that too, huh?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:09.76,Kaho,,0,0,0,,…It’s not like you were trying to hold Tsuzuri-senpai back.\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:12.08,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Please don’t say things like that.\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.63,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Kozue…senpai…?\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:45.99,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Go!\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:54.27,Kaho,,0,0,0,,…Good luck, Kozue-senpai.\N{\fs45}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:14.87,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I’m sorry.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.04,0:00:36.87,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Tsuzuri.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.61,0:01:15.34,Kozue,,0,0,0,,What?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:27.41,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I… suppose so, yes.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:33.49,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Haa…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:38.51,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Is it because I mentioned getting scouted earlier?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:42.27,Kozue,,0,0,0,,If that’s your concern, you should know that my stance on it hasn’t changed.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:46.24,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I said it earlier, and I’ll say it again. I’m not going anywhere.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.81,0:01:57.25,Kozue,,0,0,0,,You’ve been going on and on about “how I feel” this whole time.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:02:00.71,Kozue,,0,0,0,,What, are you saying that you know how I feel better than I do…!?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:10.71,Kozue,,0,0,0,,And again, I said that I won’t be leaving!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:19.64,Kozue,,0,0,0,,What are you… talking about…?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:35.33,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That’s not…!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:39.50,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…how I feel, I’m pretty sure…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:45.08,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:49.40,Kozue,,0,0,0,,always have that answer for myself.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:53.81,Kozue,,0,0,0,,So even if you say that you don’t believe I’m okay–\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:21.86,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Tsuzuri, I…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.63,0:04:07.56,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…It seems you’ve seen something quite unfortunate.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:31.16,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Kaho-san…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:32.94,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:42.01,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’m okay… \NI’m completely fine.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:14.56,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…This is actually the second time someone in the club has been scouted by another school.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.77,0:05:18.54,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:24.30,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It was at the end of last year, just before the Love Live! regionals.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:29.17,Kozue,,0,0,0,,The student council president came and told me herself.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:36.68,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Another School Idol Club was interested in scouting Tsuzuri.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:53.25,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…If…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:59.13,Kozue,,0,0,0,,If Tsuzuri accepts their proposal, what would happen…?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:33.04,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Sachi… senpai.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:38.83,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Is there a way… to avoid losing the club?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:53.57,Kozue,,0,0,0,,If you really think so, then you should have called Tsuzuri here instead of me.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:56.64,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:07:00.81,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I… don’t think you’ve done anything wrong, Sachi-senpai.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:05.75,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But… I can’t be sure that Tsuzuri will decline.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:08.15,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I can’t help but think…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:11.76,Kozue,,0,0,0,,If by some small chance she decides that she does want to accept…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:18.74,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That girl is very talented.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:24.25,Kozue,,0,0,0,,And it shouldn’t be my decision whether or not she’ll accept the offer.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:25.73,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:31.99,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I… I don’t want to lose the School Idol Club…!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:41.96,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Knowing you, there has to be a reason why you only called me about this. Sachi-senpai, please tell me.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:11.32,Kozue,,0,0,0,,If she was explicitly “Yugiri Tsuzuri, from the Hasunosora School Idol Club”...\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:17.99,Kozue,,0,0,0,,If that was what people thought of when they saw her, then there would be no reason for those discussions…?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:26.66,Kozue,,0,0,0,,So for example, if we were to win the Love Live! regional qualifiers, then…?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:38.31,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…My goal from the very beginning was to win Love Live!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:41.96,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Regardless of what goal I pursue, my course of action will remain the same.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:44.20,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Sachi-senpai.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:49.21,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I don’t want to lose the School Idol Club…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:54.99,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Not after I’ve made so many memories here…!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:58.18,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’ll do whatever I can to avoid that.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:12.15,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I’m sure I’ll be okay.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:16.09,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for talking to me about this.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:29.50,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I knew that at the qualifiers, as long as I danced as I expected I would…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.53,Kozue,,0,0,0,,then everything would be fine.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:35.67,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But you know, Kaho-san?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:41.12,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Even having said all that, I still couldn’t do well.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:45.23,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Sachi-senpai retired, and Megumi…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:49.17,Kozue,,0,0,0,,the other member in the club, got injured and stopped performing as a result.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:51.07,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That left just the two of us…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:54.15,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But we still decided we’d try our best…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.18,0:10:00.65,Kozue,,0,0,0,,and at that critical time, with that song Tsuzuri so spiritedly made for us…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:04.44,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I wasn’t able to dance well.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:10.80,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But I had to win, no matter what.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:12.90,Kozue,,0,0,0,,So I…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:16.98,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I decided to change our choreography at the very last minute.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:25.13,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Tsuzuri’s original idea was based on showing what we worked together to achieve.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:28.44,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I changed it to focus solely on her.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:32.50,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I thought that we would have the highest probability of winning with that.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:41.40,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Naturally, she wanted to know why I changed it.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:46.38,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But, until the very end, I dodged the question by telling her that I was okay with it.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:52.12,Kozue,,0,0,0,,And we practiced, and practiced, and practiced…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:58.84,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Yet, I never reached a level where I would be satisfied dancing next to her.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:19.10,Kozue,,0,0,0,,When we won the regional qualifiers, Tsuzuri became well-known for being “Yugiri Tsuzuri, from the Hasunosora School Idol Club.”\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:25.84,Kozue,,0,0,0,,And to ensure the club’s continued existence, I betrayed Tsuzuri…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:30.64,Kozue,,0,0,0,,So when she says she doesn’t believe my “I’m okay”,\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:33.21,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I suppose she’s right.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:35.91,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:52.90,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:55.00,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It’s just as you say.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:12:00.82,Kozue,,0,0,0,,If Tsuzuri accepted the scouting offer, then the club would have been disbanded.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:05.25,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I could have said so and used the survival of the club as leverage.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:09.87,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But there was no way I could…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:15.01,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I could never be so callous to her just for the sake of the club.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:18.62,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…No.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:23.85,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I was just thinking she would be like that.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:31.52,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she would have just shaken off those threats and left anyway.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:37.89,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Maybe in the end, I was just afraid she would respond how I would.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:58.82,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Kaho-san.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:03.59,Kozue,,0,0,0,,My goal is to win Love Live!.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:09.01,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:12.01,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I don’t think I’ve said that in a while.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:16.10,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I just noticed that I’d never even mentioned it to you.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:20.32,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Did you know?\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:23.11,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Tsuzuri didn’t have a clue what Love Live! was.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.62,0:13:28.07,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Around this time last year, I ended up showing her a wide variety of videos from Love Live!,\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:30.62,Kozue,,0,0,0,,and we were so engrossed we ended up staying up all night.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.36,Kozue,,0,0,0,,We most certainly did.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:39.40,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It feels… quite nostalgic now.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.65,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I remember it so fondly… as does Tsuzuri, I’m sure.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:49.46,Kozue,,0,0,0,,If my dream is to win Love Live!... then to achieve that dream,\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:54.61,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I should accept the offer to join a stronger School Idol Club… huh…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:59.69,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Compared to me, who may have ruined her opportunity to take a large leap forward…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.79,Kozue,,0,0,0,,She’s the exact opposite.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.03,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:20.34,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I didn’t feel like I was.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.72,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It’s much the opposite, actually…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:26.45,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I was… just…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.32,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I… see…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:35.08,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I see now…\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:39.92,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I didn’t understand anything at all…!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:44.32,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, Kaho-san! I-I have to…!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:06.60,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I am Otomune Kozue. It is a pleasure to meet you.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:10.54,Kozue,,0,0,0,,My goal… is to win Love Live!!\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:32.52,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I did it because I wanted to win.\N{\fs45}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:34.52,Kozue,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:42.77,NPC,,0,0,0,,“Our School Idol Club is interested in Yugiri Tsuzuri.\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:45.95,NPC,,0,0,0,,We believe she would draw attention as a school idol here.”\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:50.02,NPC,,0,0,0,,…That’s basically what the letter is about.\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:06.61,NPC,,0,0,0,,…If she did, I’m sure she would have a bright future as a school idol there.\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:08.43,NPC,,0,0,0,,However…\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:17.87,NPC,,0,0,0,,…The Hasunosora School Idol Club would have to be disbanded.\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:23.93,NPC,,0,0,0,,Yes, clubs are allowed to continue with very few members at this school.\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.20,NPC,,0,0,0,,But even so,\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:30.36,NPC,,0,0,0,,there’s no reasonable way a club with only one member could meet the requirements to continue.\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:34.23,NPC,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:41.44,NPC,,0,0,0,,Well…\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:45.04,NPC,,0,0,0,,If Tsuzuri says she won’t go.\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:14.75,NPC,,0,0,0,,Kozue, I…\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:33.38,NPC,,0,0,0,,Kozue…\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:45.85,NPC,,0,0,0,,…It’s just…\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:08:01.08,NPC,,0,0,0,,…That other School Idol Club said that they wanted to poach Tsuzuri from our club because Hasunosora hasn’t produced any results yet.\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:03.60,NPC,,0,0,0,,So conversely…\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:28.45,NPC,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:31.98,NPC,,0,0,0,,There would be no reason to scout her in that case.\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:04.66,NPC,,0,0,0,,…Then you’ll have to bear the weight of this conversation alone.\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:06.98,NPC,,0,0,0,,Not just now, but for a while to come.\N{\fs45}[Sachi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.36,0:00:06.32,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,They’re…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:07.98,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,no longer in sync…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:23.46,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Um…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:27.29,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Tsuzuri-senpai…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:46.78,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Good idea! \NIf there’s anything you want…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:54.13,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,U-Um, okay!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:57.21,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I’m sure you can, but…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:00:58.55,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Well…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:03.56,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,By any chance, is there anything you think you’re close to figuring out…?\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:42.84,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Ah…! Tsuzuri-senpai!\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:46.58,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,…Um…\N{\fs45}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:18.00,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,It happens.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:29.64,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…Sorry, Saya.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:31.64,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,You too, Kaho.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.77,0:00:34.12,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,This is our problem.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:48.18,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:51.75,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I’ll try to do better.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:08.66,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I think I should just go out and say it.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:13.80,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…Hey, Kozu.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.95,0:01:18.17,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,….We did really well this morning, didn’t we?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:22.66,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,We were able to talk about a lot of things.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.36,0:01:32.35,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I don’t understand what you’re feeling right now, Kozu.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.88,0:01:51.07,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…I don’t think that’s how you really feel.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:02.71,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Of course I don’t.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:07.25,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,You haven’t told me.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:15.82,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…You never tell me anything.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:24.23,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,You always keep everything to yourself.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:30.22,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,You just insist that you’re okay, and then you work yourself too hard.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:33.47,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I don’t know what to believe anymore.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:43.38,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,You’re not completely sure?\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:58.67,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,That’s another reason for me not to believe you, then.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:02.42,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…I’m leaving.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:06.49,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Your goal is to win Love Live!.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:13.15,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,And yet, you’re refusing the scouting offer, which means you’re throwing away a chance to get closer to that goal.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:17.36,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,The only “feelings” I hear from you…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:19.49,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,are just excuses.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:28.10,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I… I want to believe you.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:34.67,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,But I can’t trust your “I’m okay” anymore.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:39.45,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,And if nothing else, I’m not okay.\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.88,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,…Oh, it’s already morning…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:22.29,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I had fun, though…\N{\fs45}[Tsuzuri]
